	Plug-In specification	~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~Name:			"LHA Expander Bridge"Qualified:		RavelSHUFFLER Plug-In extractorFunction:		Expander of LHAed or LZHed arcmailRequired:		"LHA Expander" installed at start up volume(*)Configuration:	-Source code:	available(*) You must configure "LHA Expander" for extractingpackets into 'Temp' folder with suppress of creationof subfolder and delete original after expanding.NOTE: Any of plug-ins can be removed from Plug-Insfolder for disabling their function(s). It's usefulfor non-standard extractors for FIDO (why you shouldinstall all plug-ins when you certainly know thatyour uplink/downlink compress arcmail with ZIP?).